										aria-expanded="false"
										aria-label="Dropdown"
									>
										<svg
											class="me-3 block shrink-0 lg:me-2 lg:hidden"
											xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
											width="20"
											height="20"
											viewBox="0 0 256 256"
											><path
												fill="currentColor"
												d="M248 210h-18V94h2a6 6 0 0 0 0-12h-50V46h2a6 6 0 0 0 0-12H40a6 6 0 0 0 0 12h2v164H24a6 6 0 0 0 0 12h224a6 6 0 0 0 0-12M218 94v116h-36V94ZM54 46h116v164h-28v-50a6 6 0 0 0-6-6H88a6 6 0 0 0-6 6v50H54Zm76 164H94v-44h36ZM74 80a6 6 0 0 1 6-6h16a6 6 0 0 1 0 12H80a6 6 0 0 1-6-6m48 0a6 6 0 0 1 6-6h16a6 6 0 0 1 0 12h-16a6 6 0 0 1-6-6m-42 46a6 6 0 0 1 0-12h16a6 6 0 0 1 0 12Zm42-6a6 6 0 0 1 6-6h16a6 6 0 0 1 0 12h-16a6 6 0 0 1-6-6"
